mmary\n**All spec requirements are implemented.** The Dockerfiles follow the multi-stage build pattern with:\n- Builder stage: golang:1.24-alpine\n- Runtime stage: alpine:3.19\n- Non-root user (UID 1000)\n- Statically linked binaries (CGO_ENABLED=0)\n\nDocker is not available to run the actual build tests, but the code compiles and all Makefile targets are properly defined.","time":{"start":1775875411769,"end":1775875411769}}}
